devdoc.author: Okwuosa Chijioke
devdoc.details: This implements 2 ERC-20 tokens that will be minted in exactly the same proportion as the underlying ERC-20 token transferred into the Factory contract. The asset will be burned in exactly the same proportion when asked to redeem/withdrawal the underlying asset. The contract will implement periodic rebalancing
devdoc.title: ERC-20 Rebase Tokens
